videos.description: CJ McCollum uses a step-back move to create some space from Duncan Robinson, then pulls up to drain a 3-pointer for the Trail Blazers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (McCollum drains step-back 3 on Robinson) 2021/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCollum drains step-back 3 on Robinson

videos.description: Max Strus throws an alley-oop to Precious Achiuwa who goes up for a nice one-handed dunk for the Heat.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Heat's Max Strus lobs to Precious Achiuwa for sweet slam) 2021/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Heat's Max Strus lobs to Precious Achiuwa for sweet slam

videos.description: Tyler Herro dumps a pass into a cutting Bam Adebayo who takes off to deliver a two-handed stuff at the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Herro sets up Bam for the slam) 2021/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herro sets up Bam for the slam

videos.description: Gabe Vincent drives and tosses an alley-oop pass behind him to Bam Adebayo who elevates to smash down an emphatic dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bam slams down lob from Vincent) 2021/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bam slams down lob from Vincent

videos.description: Bam Adebayo goes up to grab the alley-oop pass from Tyler Herro and flies to the basket to power down a dunk with authority as the Heat take a 4th-quarter lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bam smashes emphatic alley-oop for the lead) 2021/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bam smashes emphatic alley-oop late

videos.description: CJ McCollum finds Derick Jones Jr. who goes up to stuff down an and-1 dunk right in Duncan Robinson's face to give the Trail Blazers a 121-120 lead over the Heat.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Derrick Jones Jr. dunks on Robinson for late Blazers' lead) 2021/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Derrick Jones Jr. dunks on Robinson for late Blazers' lead
